{"simplified":"想象","traditional":"想象","pinyin":"xiǎng xiàng","definitions":[{"partsOfSpeech":"动词","meaning":"to imagine; to envision","sentences":[{"simplifiedText":"我可以想象那个场景。","traditionalText":"我可以想像那個場景。","pinyin":"wǒ kěyǐ xiǎngxiàng nàgè chǎngjǐng。","translation":"I can imagine that scene.","audioPath":"/Users/johnwu/code/anki_experiment/chinese-app-prototype/.data/db/audio/7b4e33c5b2352024f75cd877738b9b19.mp3","voiceName":"zh-CN-XiaoyanNeural","tags":["EASY_TO_USE"]},{"simplifiedText":"如果你真心的去想象，你就会明白他的感受。","traditionalText":"如果你真心的去想像，你就會明白他的感受。","pinyin":"rúguǒ nǐ zhēnxīn de qù xiǎngxiàng, nǐ jiù huì míngbái tā de gǎnshòu。","translation":"If you truly imagine, you will understand his feelings.","audioPath":"zh-CN-YunyeNeural","voiceName":"/Users/johnwu/code/anki_experiment/chinese-app-prototype/.data/db/audio/8ab27e4f95643120a7853488362f2d6c.mp3","tags":["INVOLVED"]}]}]}